headline: Cadence Announces Fourth Quarter and Fiscal Year 2024 Financial Results Webcast
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., January 03, 2025--Cadence Design Systems, Inc. (Nasdaq: CDNS) will hold its fourth quarter and fiscal year 2024 financial results webcast on Tuesday, February 18, 2025
